Julie Pinson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julie_Pinson 0 Julie Pinson (born November 7, 1967) is an American actress, best known for her work with soap operas. Her best-known roles include Eve Lambert on Port Charles, Billie Reed on Days of Our Lives and Janet Ciccone on As the World Turns. Pinson also had a brief twelve-episode run as Shiloh on The Young and the Restless in 2004. She has also appeared on River Ridge as Kimberly Reeves.
